Voice Support
- [] Find voice to text library
    - [] ideally local (no API key etc)
- [] wrapper around the CLI experience

```mermaid
flowchart TD
A[Agent CLI Boots Up] --> A1[Select an Agent]
A1 -.CLI Mode.-> B[CLI listens for line of text]
B--> B1[I type]
A1 -.Voice Mode.-> C[Fire Up Voice Listening Loop]
C --> D[I talk]
D --> E[Audio streams]
E --> F[Audio becomes text buffer]
F --> F1[User presses enter]
B1 --> F1
F -.-> F2[Audio Stream stops]
F1 --> G[Text becomes Agent Input]
G --> H[Request / Response Loop Happens]
```

voice:true when you instantiate the CLI
- check for relevant API keys (if I must)
- start the agent selection
- start the voice listening loop
